            <p>Flexbox is what CSS has been sorely lacking since its inception &#8211; an easy way to create flexible web page layouts without the need for floats, clears, margin: 0 auto and JS hacks. I look forward to the day when flexbox is supported by a big enough share of the browser market to put into this all of our production sites.</p>

