        </div>

        <div class="comment-body">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2014-03-17T19:24:55+00:00">March 17, 2014</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="Justin"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> Justin</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>Simple fix I think. You need to set the container(#window) to flex so that your 2</p>
<p>&lt;ul&gt;s are flex children.</p>
<pre><code>#window { display: flex; }
</code></pre>

          </div>
        </div>
