          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2014-04-23T09:14:33+00:00">April 23, 2014</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="Chris"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> Chris</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>The .wrapper defined &#8220;-webkit-flex-flow: row wrap;&#8221; only, add &#8220;flex-flow: row wrap;&#8221; and it works in IE 11 and Firefox.</p>

