        <div class="comment-body">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2014-05-14T10:19:45+00:00">May 14, 2014</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="Ry"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> Ry</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>Great guide, nice update! Has always been very useful.</p>
<p>One thing I&#8217;ve noticed missing (here and almost every other flexbox guide) is how to do flex-grow and flex-shrink in IE10.</p>
<p>flex-grow<br />
<code>-ms-flex-positive:;</code></p>
<p>flex-shrink<br />
<code>-ms-flex-negative:;</code></p>
<p>Would be great to have this footnoted somewhere.</p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comment-actions">
          <div class="reply">
            <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-1581192' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-1581192", "1581192", "respond", "21059" )' aria-label='Reply to Ry'>Reply</a>          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      
    
