          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>try align-content: flex-start; on the container. I&#8217;m not too sure if it will help for your purpose, but with your demo it works.<br />
Also, I would rather set flex: 1 1 20%; on each sub item instead of specifying the width (again, it depends on what you want to do).</p>

