          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>I am working with flexbox on a few different projects now and love it. Only downside is all the prefixes that you need.</p>
<p>For my projects I made a less mixin stylesheet that has been tested and works in the most recent browsers (latest version -1).<br />
Hoping to help some more people out I put it on my github, so if you want a little help getting started you can grab it there <a href="https://github.com/annebosman/FlexboxLess" title="github flexboxless" rel="nofollow">github.com/annebosman/FlexboxLess</a></p>

          </div>
        </div>
