          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>the initial value of &#8216;flex-basis&#8217; is &#8216;main-size&#8217;, and if omitted in the shorthand property &#8216;flex&#8217;, it&#8217;s value is &#8216;0%&#8217;.<br />
<a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/#propdef-flex-basis" rel="nofollow">http://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/#propdef-flex-basis</a></p>

          </div>
        </div>
