        <div class="comment-body">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2014-11-03T18:13:58+00:00">November 3, 2014</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="yan"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> yan</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>The specification says <code>flex: auto</code> is <code>flex: 1 1 main-size</code>,   to be distinguished from <code>flex: 1 1 auto</code>.  Currently only Firefox  34+  support &#8216;main-size&#8217;.<br />
<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/CSS/flex-basis" rel="nofollow">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/CSS/flex-basis</a></p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comment-actions">
