            <p>I notice that the 3 column demo at the end is not working and should there be more content in the sidebars than the one word shown then the columns stretch to 100% width and break the layout.</p>
<p>The width of the side columns need to be set.</p>
<p>e.g.</p>
<pre><code>@media all and (min-width: 600px) {
  .aside {
    flex: 1 0 0;
  }
}

</code></pre>

