        <div class="comment-body">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2015-08-17T16:24:19+00:00">August 17, 2015</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="Kp"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> Kp</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>In the event anybody is having issues getting it to work on firefox for the 2nd example (tomato background)</p>
<p>Put the flex items into their own container with no other element in them.<br />
Add * flex-flow: row wrap; * to .flex-container</p>
<p>Hope this helps.</p>

          </div>
        </div>
