        </div>

        <div class="comment-body">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-time"><time datetime="2015-10-15T08:56:02+00:00">October 15, 2015</time></div> <div class="comment-author"><a href="Alex"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> Alex</div>
            
          </div>
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>flex-basis seems to have got some updates, <code>main-size</code> no longer exists, <code>auto</code> means look at width / height property (previously main-size),  new <code>content</code> keyword means automatic sizing (previously auto)</p>
<p><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/flex-basis" rel="nofollow">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/flex-basis</a></p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comment-actions">
          <div class="reply">
